  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety Study of Clonidine Lauriad® to Treat Oral Mucositis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase II, Multi-center, Randomised, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled Study Comparing the Efficacy and Safety of Clonidine Lauriad® 50 μg and 100 μg Mucoadhesive Buccal Tablet (MBT) Applied Once Daily to Those of Placebo in the Prevention and Treatment of Chemoradiation Therapy Induced Oral Mucositis in Patients With Head and Neck Cancer</official_title>
  <sponsors>
