  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the efficacy and safety of Clonidine Lauriad® to
      treat chemoradiation therapy induced severe oral mucositis in patients with head and neck
      cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
